English: Bulkhead Door locked, can only be unlocked with {0}
Description:
Don't localize Bulkhead Door.
A text that appears on screen when the player is standing next to a locked bulkhead door, informing them that it can only be unlocked with a certain key. "{0}" will be replaced by the ID of the key, do not alter those characters.
